# Entrogenics CORE - Git Attributes

# Enforce UTF-8 encoding for all text files to preserve symbolic glyphs (✡, ☉)
* text=auto eol=lf

# Markdown files
*.md text diff=markdown

# HTML files
*.html text diff=html

# CSS files
*.css text diff=css

# JavaScript files
*.js text diff=javascript

# JSON files
*.json text

# Plain text files
*.txt text

# SVG files (treat as text for proper diff)
*.svg text

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary

# Archives
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.rar binary

# Ensure critical Entrogenic symbol files are never mangled
*.md linguist-language=Markdown
CORE_THESIS.md linguist-language=Markdown
